attributes.description: Kafka analysis of topics and consumer groups

params.markdown:
### Overview

This dashboard provides visibility into the overall health and activity of the Kafka cluster.  

- Summarizes key cluster metrics such as brokers, topics, partitions, replicas, and consumer groups.  
- Tracks consumer partition reassignments and offset progress over time.  
- Highlights broker-level details including leader partitions and replica counts.  
- Provides topic-level insights with partition, replica, consumer, and offset information.  
- Surfaces consumer group lag and client-specific partition activity.
